Package: conquer
Type: Package
Title: Convolution-type smoothed quantile regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-03-06
Author: Xiaoou Pan, Kean Ming Tan, Wen-Xin Zhou
Maintainer: Xiaoou Pan <xip024@ucsd.edu>
Description: Performs convolution-type smoothed quantile regression (conquer) implemented via Barzilai-Borwein gradient descent with Huber warm initialization.
             It achieves evidently fast computational speed while maintaining estimation accuracy, comparing with classical quantile regression.
             The package also includes statistical inference via multiplier bootstrap for conquer.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C++11
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.3), matrixStats, stats
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
